# Testing Rules

All functionality must include tests.

Test Types

Unit Test
Component Test
Integration Test
E2E Test

---

# Coverage Requirement

Minimum coverage requirements:

Lines: 90%+
Functions: 90%+
Branches: 85%+
Statements: 90%+

Code changes must not be accepted if coverage fails.

---

# Test Rules

Every function must have tests.

Feature implementations must include tests.

Tests must run automatically.

Prefer colocated tests:

feature/tests
component.test.ts
